om/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Spotify-on-a-computer-Photo-by-Klaudia-Radecka_NurPhoto-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Spotify-on-a-computer-Photo-by-Klaudia-Radecka_NurPhoto-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Spotify-on-a-computer-Photo-by-Klaudia-Radecka_NurPhoto-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Spotify-on-a-computer-Photo-by-Klaudia-Radecka_NurPhoto-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Spotify-on-a-computer-Photo-by-Klaudia-Radecka_NurPhoto-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Spotify-on-a-computer-Photo-by-Klaudia-Radecka_NurPhoto-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><div class="skin-ad-container"><div class="skin-ad-main"><p> <a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/tag/spotify">Spotify</a>现已正式取消平台上所有流媒体数量少于 1000 首的歌曲。 </p><div id="js-infinity"><div class="d-grid d-grid--focal"><div class="grid__item grid__item--main"><div class="rich-text"><div class="copy rich-text__block rich-text__block--full"><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/artists-music-2023-challenges-2024-hopes-streaming-gigs-payment-blur-easy-life-cherise-lvra-get-cape-fac-3565687">艺术家谈 2023 年的挑战和 2024 年的希望：“我只想看到我们通过销售唱片获得报酬”</a></strong></li></ul><p>该政策于 4 月 1 日推出，此前这家流媒体巨头去年发布了一份报告《 <em><a href="https://artists.spotify.com/en/blog/modernizing-our-royalty-system" target="_blank" rel="noopener">现代化我们的版税系统</a></em>》，其中首次出现了有关该决定的消息。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/spotify-confirm-songs-now-need-at-least-1000-streams-to-earn-royalties-3546548">该平台已计划此举有一段时间了</a>。</p><p>新规定出台之前，几个月来人们一直猜测该流媒体服务将推出新政策，包括有传言称该公司将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/spotify-announce-profit-and-millions-more-subscribers-but-also-royalty-cuts-to-less-popular-tracks-3521362">让艺术家更难从他们的音乐中获得版税</a>。</p><p>根据 Spotify 的数据，该服务上约有 1 亿首歌曲，但只有约 3750 万首歌曲满足新的创收要求。</p><p>这意味着大约 60% 的曲目将不符合新的门槛，尽管 Spotify 确实记得这些歌曲只占该服务流媒体总数的不到 1%。</p><p> Spotify 表示，该平台上 99.5% 的流媒体“都是流媒体数量超过 1,000 条的曲目”。他们接着声称，取消曲目的货币化不会导致“支付给版权持有者的音乐版税池的规模发生变化”。</p><p>它辩称，相反，它将“每年使用数千万美元来增加对所有符合条件的曲目的付款，而不是将其分散到 0.03 美元的付款中。”</p><p> Spotify 还表示，如果要收取版税，现在需要达到最低数量的唯一听众数量——在检测到欺诈活动增加后，采取这一措施是为了阻止虚假流媒体的增加。 </p><figure id="attachment_3546551" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3546551" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3546551" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spotify@2000x1270.jpg" alt="智能手机屏幕上显示的 Spotify 徽标 库存图片" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spotify@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spotify@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spotify@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spotify@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spotify@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spotify@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3546551" class="wp-caption-text">智能手机屏幕上显示的 Spotify 徽标 库存图像。图片来源：Nikolas Kokovlis/NurPhoto 来自 Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>去年年底， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/spotify-announces-cut-of-1500-jobs-with-17-per-cent-of-workforce-facing-axe-3552871">Spotify 宣布将裁员 17%，以节省成本</a>。此前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/spotify-to-cut-six-per-cent-of-workforce-3385265">该公司曾决定在 2023 年初再裁员 6%</a> ，当时该公司称此举是为了提升“速度”。</p><p>首席执行官丹尼尔·埃克(Daniel Ek)表示，由于经济增长“急剧放缓”，他做出了“艰难”的决定。 Spotify 拥有约 9,000 名员工，这意味着在本轮裁员中预计将失去 1,500 个工作岗位。</p><p>这一消息令一些人感到意外，因为就在几个月前， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/spotify-announce-profit-and-millions-more-subscribers-but-also-royalty-cuts-to-less-popular-tracks-3521362">该公司刚刚宣布第三季度利润好于预期</a>，用户数量增加了 600 万。</p><p>一月份， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/spotify-seemingly-confirms-superfan-clubs-coming-to-platform-3578699">Spotify 似乎还暗示“超级粉丝俱乐部”功能可能很快就会推出</a>。</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/spotify-has-now-officially-demonetised-all-songs-with-less-than-1000-streams-3614010">Spotify 现已正式取消所有流媒体数量少于 1,000 首的歌曲的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
